data.description: Coveted North Durham location! This charming brick ranch seamlessly blends traditional charm with modern upgrades. The semi-open layout includes a formal dining room, living room, den, and a remodeled open kitchen with high-end granite waterfall countertops. New luxury vinyl plank flooring, elegantly renovated bathrooms, and a fresh interior/exterior coat of paint elevate the overall allure. Nestled on a private, spacious lot with a fenced yard and no HOA, this 2-bedroom (3 bedrooms, but septic is for 2) home is just minutes from Eno River Park, major highways, restaurants, and shopping. A perfect fusion of character and contemporary living – your new home awaits! **Seller is offering a roof allowance with an acceptable offer.** Potential to add a shower in the primary bath!
